# Input

```svelte
<div {@attach myAttachment}>...</div>
<button {@attach tooltip(content)}>
	Hover me
</button>
<canvas
	width={32}
	height={32}
	{@attach (canvas) => {
		const context = canvas.getContext('2d');

		$effect(() => {
			context.fillStyle = color;
			context.fillRect(0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height);
		});
	}}
></canvas>

```


